description.narrative: UNICEF continued to strengthen and apply cross sectoral strategies like gender, innovations and communication for development across all programmes. Emergency preparedness and response was strengthened providing lifesaving services to over 230,000 refugees in three camps in the Kigoma region and communication for development strategies were applied across all programmes. Innovative approaches continued to be applied across UNICEFs sectoral programme with 27 young people benefiting from seed funding as part of the Generation Unlimited initiative. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:16/01/2020
